abstract: New York City Council Speaker Christine C Quinn says she is not 'anti-Wall Street,' but anger of Occupy Wall Street protesters should not be ignored.
snippet: Christine C. Quinn, the City Council speaker, said that she was not “anti-Wall Street” but that the anger of the Occupy Wall Street protesters should not be ignored.
lead_paragraph: Christine C. Quinn, the City Council speaker, said that she was not “anti-Wall Street” but that the anger of the Occupy Wall Street protesters should not be ignored.

headline.main: Quinn Says City Must Find Balance in Response to Protests
headline.print_headline: Quinn Says City Must Find Balance in Response to Protests
headline.seo: Christine Quinn Wants Balanced Response to Occupy Wall Street
